\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 SurfaceLength3D Xcode Project Setup
\b0\fs24 \
\
The project needs to have the VTK libraries added to it as well as knowing where to find the VTK header files.\
\

\b Step 1
\b0  - Clear my settings
\b \

\b0 \
Clear the library and header search paths from the project I sent you (as the paths will differ between our systems). \
To do this:\
\
a) Display the Target Info window (use Xcode's menu Project->Edit Active Target "SurfaceLength3D") and select the Build tab and Deployment configuration.\
\
b) Type "search" into the target info search bar to narrow the list down.\
\
c) You will either see entries for "Header Search Paths" and "Library Search Paths" or as user-define LIBRARY_SEARCH_PATHS......\
Clear these search paths.\
\
